author: Jason Brennan
title: Life | Pics: McDonald's are bringing out sweet potato fries so everything's right with the world
text:
We've waited too long for this.
Unfortunately we, as in the Irish, might have to wait a little longer.
McDonald's have announced the introduction of sweet potato fries to the US market for a trial period this week, but there's been no world of whether or not they'll be added to the menu on this side of the Atlantic.
Riot, anyone for a riot? IS THERE ANYTHING TO BE SAID FOR A RIOT?
